00:31:03.730 --> 00:31:04.730
What is it?

00:31:04.730 --> 00:31:07.569
Short-sightedness or near-sightedness.

00:31:07.569 --> 00:31:10.930
In other words, a person can see very clearly

00:31:10.930 --> 00:31:13.369
what is just around them,

00:31:13.369 --> 00:31:16.329
